Sunday Talk: October 20, 2013

The GOP was out in full force on Sunday, as the talk shows did postmortems on the government shutdown. The only thing Mitch McConnell, John McCain, Marco Rubio, and Ted Cruz agreed on was their dislike of Obamacare. So the question is, what’s next for the GOP?
